ZOO

Bomb/Defuse Map for Counter-Strike: Source

CS:GO original map creators: Squad & Yanzl
CS:S map editor: Niko
Navigation Mesh editor: Meurglis3

High quality port for CS:S of a sunny atmospheric same-named map for CS:GO by Squad & Yanzl.
Several areas with different themes set inside a San Franciscan zoo.

Story: 
Terrorists are on a mission to bring mayhem to the Bay Area Zoo.

P.S. ~  Catch Me A Colobus :-)
